'''Rokna tree fungus'''<ref name="TSD">{{Ewoks|To Save Deej}}</ref> or '''rokna fungus'''<ref name="G9">{{GamerCite|9|Endor and the Moddell Sector}}</ref> was a deadly, blue fungus that grew on the [[rokna tree]]<ref name="TSDb">[[To Save Deej (book)|''To Save Deej'' picture book]]</ref> found on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. The sharp points protruding from this fungus could cause the death of those coming in contact with them.<ref name="TSD" /> The highly addictive [[Spice/Legends|spice]] known as [[Rokna Blue|rokna blue]] was derived from rokna fungus.<ref name="G9" /> The [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Deej Warrick]] once cut his arm on some rokna fungus.<ref name="TSD" />

{{Flora-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The [[To Save Deej (book)|''To Save Deej'' storybook]] spells the fungus's name as "rockna."

